originalText.text: Ronee has been an instrumental part of my healing and growing process. She has walked me through my process of trauma recovery and helped me learn coping skills that are helpful for the rest of my life. She listens, makes an effort to understand each situation and has so much wisdom to connect the pieces needed for healing. I'm grateful she helped me to find my voice! I would highly recommend her to anyone who is ready to do the emotional work.

originalText.text: Ronee Miller is a much-needed therapist with keen wisdom in therapeutic counseling. She has shown to be amazing in addressing disappointing experiences and revealing how they can impede and ruin a fulfilling and satisfying life. My personal experience with her has always been found to be enlightening and freeing. She has help me to deal with my past, understanding it from a different retrospective filled with hope. One of her many counsels I respect the most " do something about it". I recommend Ronee Miller and thank her for her passionate and encouraging care.

originalText.text: Ronee is an amazing professional. I have seen Ronee for many years, and with her help, I was able work through a difficult time in my life. She is never afraid of telling me the truth, even when it is not what I wanted to hear at the moment,  this was very helpful to my treatment. She genuinely cares for her patients, and that makes a world of difference.  She’s a very dedicated person and has a plethora of knowledge that she is always willing to share. Thank you so much, Ronee. I appreciate everything that you have done for me. You have definitely been a blessing in my life, and a contributor to my personal and emotional health and growth, very grateful to have met you.

originalText.text: I did not believe in therapy!  However, Ronee turned me into a believer. Ronee is passionate about helping others to get victory in their lives.  She is present, compassionate, caring, professional, experienced and filled with wisdom.  Ronee helped me discover the person I was created to be. Thank you Ronee!!!

originalText.text: Ronee is a gifted therapist in every way, and her home practice is an environment where true healing can happen. The hard work and time and money that go into therapy are no joke, and Ronee honors your investment in yourself with her thoughful, caring approach. Plus, her dog is so cute!
